{"tid":2508498,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉率眾搞大型藝員面試 應徵者鬧爆被當佈景板做騷","createTime":"2021-04-28T21:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T21:41:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f3f8757f59d34ddfc1607bf004609492a66a79","tid":2508498,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:29:38.000Z","msg":"今日TVB在將軍澳電視城舉行「藝員及電視製作人員訓練班」面試，大台高層副總經理曾志偉、集團首席創意官王祖藍等都有出席，還大鑼大鼓邀請傳媒到場採訪，曾志偉等人輪住上台發言，面試如同開記招。而曾志偉更豪言，要將藝訓班變成類似ViuTV《全民造星》真人騷，連培訓過程都要擺出來給觀眾睇。<br />\n<br />\n講還講，但今日一班面試者，就有不同的感受。有份參與今日面試的網民，隨即在討論區出post鬧爆大台，網民指︰「真係一肚氣，等又等得耐，每人得15秒有啲搵笨，仲要講講吓嘢俾人打斷。」有網民抱不平謂︰「只（得）15秒，睇一個人適唔適合做藝員？黐線！」有另一位網民就回應道︰「我去面試嘅遭遇唔同你嘅，你有無去錯地方？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210428/XWJY325QRRE6PL22HRSUDX7LFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210428%2FXWJY325QRRE6PL22HRSUDX7LFE%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzRlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=1a504dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210428%2FXWJY325QRRE6PL22HRSUDX7LFE%2F&h=e79d8816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210428/XWJY325QRRE6PL22HRSUDX7LFE/</a>"},{"pid":"bfa00cd0f313a06526f6979853ef406114d4d95c","tid":2508498,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:32:55.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨"},{"pid":"fa9b55fa7ef2c9c96acd2cdbad9796da7c9361e0","tid":2508498,"uid":156936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:33:59.000Z","msg":"有網民問有無去錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n居然會去tvb interview<br />\n已經唔係錯地方咁簡單<br />\n係成個人價值觀是非觀都錯撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d963b0bc0e17beb0eefe48e1119a2777b533cc9","tid":2508498,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:34:56.000Z","msg":"即係咁，唔好係tvb就鬧爆住<br />\n但你都做啲成績出嚟先做noise丫，啲咁嘅垃